Added a titles system:
Titles are obtained by completing secret tasks in the game, such as completing a raid in under 5 minutes.
They are displayed next to your chat name. Example: ["Demon Eye"][mygame43]: Erin!!!
Titles that are harder to obtain will have custom colors.
Find the new NPC to see a list of all available titles. Currently, there are more than 100 of them.
Added the Ghoul race:
V1: Becomes stronger during the night (increased speed and health regen).
V2: Unlocks the ability to life leech.
V3: User gains increased damage, defense, and speed. Moves have 40% less cooldown. Lasts 8 seconds.
Nerfed Quake V2:
Added some ending lag to the Z when it lands.
Longer X and C wind up.
